look very impressive. It automatically generates a table of contents, which with a single puzzle

00:08:47.840 --> 00:08:54.599
is just, like, okay. But you can imagine that with 20 puzzles or even with five puzzles,

00:08:54.599 --> 00:09:00.320
having something that just automatically generates is a saves you a lot of work. And so the idea

00:09:00.320 --> 00:09:04.880
behind this is really that we set up a lot of things for you in advance, and when your

00:09:04.880 --> 00:09:11.179
project is small, it feels like just extra work. But we're setting you up to really easily

