we have a test case. We have a sample of the data, the answer to that sample, and that

00:10:40.539 --> 00:10:46.520
way you can start out by writing a script that works for the sample. And in the case

00:10:46.520 --> 00:10:50.619
of small datasets, maybe it doesn't make a big difference, but you can imagine that if

